$interpreted: Lucky: ... Curses. Bribed and settled down all those damn nobles and only now they tell me the papers don't match?
Lucky: Finally got the recipe nailed down too. All I'm missing now is a factory...
Little Boy: ... Sir, do you have some food you can give us?
Little Girl: We're starving. Please sir...
Lucky: Little demihuman beggars from the Slums?
Lucky: Bug off. I don't have anything!
Little Boy: Please sir... I have siblings to take care of...

Lucky: Let go, you're messing up my clothes!
You goat-horned scum!
Little Boy: Whaaaah!

Lucky: Bastard, such a god-awful day it's been...
I'll teach you demihuman beggars a lesson!
Lucky: Get over here!
Little Girl: No... no... AHHHHHH!

Little Boy: What are you doing to Eve, let her go!
UGH!
Hyacinthus: Eve!
Eve: Cin, what's up?
Hyacinthus: Finally found you. Did you know about the incident at the plaza this morning? It was terrible!
Eve: What happened?
Hyacinthus: Jim suddenly lost his mind and started attacking people, then a packet of powder fell out of his pocket.
Hyacinthus: But Nigel told me to stay out of it...
Eve: I still have some things to tend to. Need to go.
Hyacinthus: Where are you going?
Eve: Going to say hi to a "friend".

Noble's Bodyguard: Stop! Put that thing down!
Don't let her escape!
Lucky: Damnit! Get the blueprints back, no matter what!
Eve: This... I must take this back and show Nigel.
